PatientCitySearchParameter

Parameter address-city:string

Searches based on the patient's recorded city/village of address eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Patient?address-city={city}

ResourcePatient
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesPatient
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
